# Ceremonialist Management System - Implementation Plan

This system will be a robust, minimalist, and reliable tool for Ceremonialists to manage clients, events, and vendors. It uses a "rustic" design aesthetic and a "back-to-basics" no-build architecture for maximum reliability and ease of use.

## Design Aesthetic: "Rustic & Minimalist"
- **Color Palette**: Cream/Off-white background (`#FCF9F2`), Dark Espresso text (`#2C2925`), Muted Sage accents (`#84A98C`).
- **Typography**: Serif headers (Playfair Display) and clean body text.
- **Visuals**: Clean lines, generous whitespace, subtle paper-like textures (via CSS).

## Proposed Changes

### Core Architecture
The system will use **Vanilla JS** with **ESM modules**. Data will be persisted in `localStorage`.

